#: ../../index.rst:4
msgid "FreeRec 是一个基于 PyTorch 的推荐系统库，提供从数据预处理到模型训练的全流程支持。"
msgstr ""
"FreeRec is a PyTorch-based recommendation system library that provides "
"end-to-end support from data preprocessing to model training."

#: ../../index.rst:11
msgid "核心特性"
msgstr "Key Features"

#: ../../index.rst:13
msgid "**数据处理流水线** — 内置 30+ 公开数据集，一键完成拆分与过滤"
msgstr ""
"**Data Processing Pipeline** -- Built-in 30+ public datasets with one-"
"command splitting and filtering"

#: ../../index.rst:14
msgid "**模型架构基类** — 通用推荐、序列推荐、评分预测等基类，快速搭建模型"
msgstr ""
"**Model Architecture Base Classes** -- Base classes for general "
"recommendation, sequential recommendation, rating prediction, etc., "
"enabling rapid model development"

#: ../../index.rst:15
msgid "**丰富的评估指标** — Precision、Recall、NDCG、AUC 等 20+ 指标"
msgstr ""
"**Rich Evaluation Metrics** -- 20+ metrics including Precision, Recall, "
"NDCG, AUC, and more"

#: ../../index.rst:16
msgid "**灵活的训练框架** — YAML 配置驱动，支持分布式训练与超参搜索"
msgstr ""
"**Flexible Training Framework** -- YAML configuration-driven, with "
"support for distributed training and hyperparameter search"

#: ../../index.rst:17
msgid "**可选图神经网络** — 集成 PyG，支持图推荐模型（如 LightGCN）"
msgstr ""
"**Optional Graph Neural Networks** -- Integrated with PyG, supporting "
"graph-based recommendation models (e.g., LightGCN)"

